name: A Reminder.
description: A reminder that YOU are loved. Always.

attributes.value: This little token is a reminder that YOU have value, that YOU are worth it, and that YOU ARE LOVED! Always.

1. Close your eyes. 2. Inhale slowly through your nose while speaking the names of loved ones in your head (Yourself included!). 3. Exhale slowly through your mouth. 4. Repeat steps 1-3 five times. 5. Open your eyes.
Send this to someone you think could use a little reminder that they are loved. You can always mint more ü§ó
